.000Z","msg":"重點：希望美國慎重考慮，三思而行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講完又講 又話打爛人地排牙又剩 條線就快縮到入地核<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed320733ed7735e338c889763c9e343d82254793","tid":603481,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"納dee 又發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695909a54b41b7deabd614dcf2278b9bc77c1c9b","tid":603481,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"中國有冇搞清楚自由貿易呢個問題上面邊一方先係報復嗰個呀？我睇佢又扮無辜喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2533627a844b83a070880d91780941e5a93e450a","tid":603481,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T00:54:55.000Z","msg":"蟲國想人地點負責？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a2fabff367d63376430e8ea285fb00308e7a81","tid":603481,"uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:15:23.000Z","msg":"百害而無一利啵，咪姐係加速你既最大假想敵收皮<br />\n假想敵自殺你唔係應該開心先係既咩？"},{"pid":"dd7642d4a4f40ace1251ced1277405c18b131991","tid":603481,"uid":44698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"美帝都簽署晒仲口交<br />\n<br />\n永遠死淨把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0a0bece5f9f556e46bdb13d3e3111420a647ec","tid":603481,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0916e1d83113260830c40f07477432b2df72203","tid":603481,"uid":41545,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T19:25:30.000Z","msg":"未打就已經淆晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" c